--> Functional and Non-Functional Requirements that we want this platform to support.

1.) Functional Requirements: a.) Tweet b.) Re-tweet c.) Follow d.) Search
 Search: for some particular content within all the tweets that have been posted on the twitter.
 This would be usually to do some trend analysis or to figure out what's happening in the world etc


2.) Non Functional: a.) Read heavy b.) Fast Rendering c.) Fast tweet d.) Lag OK in some cases e.) Scale

Scale: As of 18-June-2021
https://www.internetlivestats.com/twitter-statistics/
~150 Million DAU, ~350 Million MAU, 1.5 Billion Accounts, 500 Million tweets/day = 5700 tweets/s:12000 @peak
	